description:
Responsibilities
Direct report to team manager for daily operations in assigned south east Asia channels such as Shopee and Lazada;
Assist in the business activities and projects of assigned channels including but not limited to order management, fulfillment, order forecast, inventory management, preparing business analysis reports;
Manage product mix and assortment planning on assigned platforms;
Analyze business trends and consumer insights and evaluate existing product categories on choices;
Conduct marketing research, analysis and routine data reports;
Liaise and coordinate with buyers, logistics and related departments on day to day business operation.
Requirements

University graduate with at least 2 years’ experience in eCommerce / retail management preferred;
Good numerical sense;
Proficiency in MS Office including MS Excel;
Hard-working with positive attitude;
Able to work under pressure and meet the deadlines;
Experienced in cross-border marketplaces and eCommerce operations is absolutely advantage;
Detail-oriented, with a high level of accuracy and ability to process and analyze data;
Fast learner and willing to face challenges;
Strong communication in written and spoken English, Cantonese, with Putonghua is an advantage;
Fresh Graduate will also be considered.


We offer


5 - day work week
Medical Benefits
Annual Merit Bonus
Staff Purchase Discounts
Staff Recreation Activity
Shuttle Bus Service
Education Sponsorship

Interested parties please send a full resume with current and expected salary by email by clicking APPLY NOW:

Human Resources Department
Sa Sa Cosmetic Co Ltd
14/F, Block B, MP Industrial Centre
18 Ka Yip Street
Chai Wan
Hong Kong

